    <p>Kiss My Keto takes the MCT oil approach to ketone support — medium-chain triglycerides are rapidly transported to the liver and converted to ketones without requiring the full beta-oxidation pathway. The C8 (caprylic acid) fraction is the most ketogenic MCT, converting to BHB most efficiently. At zero sugar, 1g net carbs, and five genuinely delicious fruit flavors, Kiss My Keto solves the "keto snack" problem that plagues many dieters. MCT-based gummies are also gentler on the stomach than BHB salt gummies.</p>

